ASoC: rsnd: add rsnd_ssi_busif_err_status_clear()

Current ssi.c clears BUSIF error status at __rsnd_ssi_interrupt(),
but its code is verbose.
This patch off-load it to rsnd_ssi_busif_err_status_clear().

